  "image_directives": "clean editorial pilates photography. Reformers on light wood floors, springs and straps in frame, instructor cueing a footbar setup. Small classes, six clients max, real practitioners in muted-tone activewear. Avoid bright commercial-gym lighting and fitness-influencer angles. No backbend hero shots. Show the carriage moving, the foot in the strap, the hand on the rib. Daylight or warm tungsten, never neon.",
